    <lb n="1"/>τῷ δεσπό<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">τῃ μ</supplied>ου καὶ ἀδελφῷ 

    <lb n="2"/><app type="BL"><lem resp="1.214">Ἰσι<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">δω</supplied>ρῳ Σίων</lem><rdg><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="15" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>ων</rdg></app> χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>πρὸ μὲν <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">πά</supplied>ντων εὔχομαι τῷ ὑψίστῳ Θε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ῷ</supplied> περὶ 

    <lb n="4"/>τῆς σῆς <choice><corr>ὑγιείας</corr><sic>υγιας</sic></choice> καὶ ὁλοκληρίας, ἵνα <choice><corr>ὑγιαίνοντα</corr><sic>υγιενοντα</sic></choice> σε καὶ 

    <lb n="5"/>εὐθυμοῦντα ἀπολάβῃ τὰ παρ᾽ ἐμοῦ <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.214">γράμματα</lem><rdg>γραμματί<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">δ</supplied>ια</rdg></app>. 

    <lb n="6"/>γνῶναί σε θέλω, κύριέ μου ἄδελφε, ὅτι ἀπῆλθεν Εὐσέ-

    <lb n="7"/>βιος εἰς τὴν κώμην εἰς τὸ γεώργιον καὶ οὐχ <subst><add place="inline">εὗρ<add place="supralinear">ε</add>ν</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">ευρ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear>ν</del></subst> το<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὺς</unclear> 

    <lb n="8"/><app type="BL"><lem resp="1.214">μόσχους</lem><rdg><gap reason="illegible" extent="2" unit="character"/>οσχουσ</rdg></app> ἐν τῷ γεωργίῳ ἐργαζομένους οὔτε τὰ <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.214">Γενναδίου</lem><rdg>Γε<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ρασ</unclear>τί<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>υ</rdg></app> 

    <lb n="9"/>οὔτε τὰ Δικαιάρχου· ἀλλὰ <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.214"><add place="supralinear">καὶ <sic>ει</sic></add> εἶπον</lem><rdg>εἷ<add place="supralinear">κα</add> <add place="supralinear">ει</add> σὺν</rdg></app> Διδύμῳ ὅτι· <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.214">δὸς τοὺς μισθο<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ὺς</supplied></lem><rdg>δούλους <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">μισ</unclear>θώ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">σῃ</supplied></rdg></app> 

    <lb n="10"/>ἄλλους, ἵνα ἐ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ρ</supplied>γάσωσιν. εἶπέν μοι ὅτι · ἀργύρια οὐκ <app type="BL"><lem resp="6.60">ἔχ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">μεν</supplied></lem><rdg>ἔχε<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ις</supplied></rdg></app>, 

    <lb n="11"/>καὶ εἰ <add place="supralinear">μὲν</add> θέλεις με ἀπελθεῖν ἐκεῖ καὶ μισθῶσαι ἐργάτας, 

    <lb n="12"/>καὶ σὺν αὐτοῖς ἐργάσομαι καὶ καθαρίσομεν τὸ γεώργι<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ο</supplied>ν. 

    <lb n="13"/>ἀντίγραψόν μοι, ἀλλ᾽ ὅρα μὴ ἀμελήσῃς ἀντιγράψαι μοι 

    <lb n="14"/>περὶ τούτου. οἶδας γάρ, ὅτι καιρός ἐστιν. γνῶθι δέ, κύρι-

    <lb n="15"/>έ μου ἄδελφε, ὅτι ὁ ἀδελφός σου ἦλθεν ἀπὸ τ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ο</unclear>[ῦ <app type="BL"><lem resp="6.60"><seg cert="low" part="N">κομι]-

    <lb n="16"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="low">τ</unclear>ά<unclear reason="undefined" cert="low">τ</unclear>ου</seg></lem><rdg><gap reason="lost" extent="5" unit="character"/>πάγου</rdg></app> ἔχων πραιποσιτούρα<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ν</supplied>, εἰς τὴν Ὄασιν εὐθὺ 

    <lb n="17"/>καὶ <app type="BL"><lem resp="6.60">ε<gap reason="illegible" extent="3" unit="character"/> <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">πά</unclear>ρεστιν</lem><rdg>ἐν αὐτῇ ἐστιν</rdg></app> · ἀπήντησεν δὲ <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ε</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ἰς</unclear> <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.214"><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/> τῇ τρια-

    <lb n="18"/>καδι</lem><rdg><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">αὐτὴν</unclear> τῇ <num value="10">ι</num></rdg></app> τοῦ Ἐπεὶφ μηνός. ἀσπάζ<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ομ</supplied>έν σε <choice><corr>πάντας</corr><sic>παντες</sic></choice> <choice><corr>τοὺς</corr><sic>οι</sic></choice> ἐν <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ῇ</supplied> 

    <lb n="19"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">οἰκ</supplied>ίᾳ μικρούς τε καὶ μεγάλους. <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.215"><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">κατ</supplied> ὄνομα</lem><rdg><add place="supralinear"><gap reason="lost" extent="3" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>νο<gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/></add></rdg></app> γνῶθι δὲ, κύριέ μο<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">υ</supplied> 

    <lb n="20"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ἄ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ε</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">λφ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ε</supplied>, διὰ τί ἀλόγως <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.215">ἀπαιδι<gap reason="lost" extent="4" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σ</unclear>ας αὐτῷ</lem><rdg>ἀπ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear>ι<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τ</unclear>η<gap reason="lost" extent="4" unit="character"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">σ</unclear>ας <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">α</unclear>ὐτό</rdg></app>. ἀν<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">τίγ</unclear><supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ρα</supplied>-

    <lb n="21"/><unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ψ</unclear>όν μοι περὶ ὧν βούλῃ καὶ <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.215"><seg cert="low" part="N"><choice><corr>μὴ</corr><sic>με</sic></choice> μεριμν<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">ή</supplied>σῃς περὶ <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">ἡ</supplied><unclear reason="undefined" cert="low">μῶν</unclear></seg></lem><rdg>μεμ<unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">φιω</unclear>ν<gap reason="lost" extent="2" unit="character"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/>ῃς περὶ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">ὧν</unclear> <gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/><gap reason="lost" extent="2" unit="character"/></rdg></app>, 

    <lb n="22"/>οὐδεὶς <supplied reason="lost" cert="high">γ</supplied>ὰρ ἐνοχλεῖ ἡμῖν, οὔτε <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.215">Ζωσί<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">μ</supplied>ῳ</lem><rdg>Ζώσι<supplied reason="lost" cert="high">μ</supplied>οσ</rdg></app> περὶ <unclear reason="undefined" cert="high">δ</unclear>ημοσίων 

    <lb n="23"/><gap reason="illegible" extent="4" unit="character"/>ν<gap reason="illegible" extent="1" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="24"/>ἐρρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι 

    <lb n="25"/>πολλοῖς χρόνοις, 

    <lb n="26"/>κύριέ μου ἄδελφε. 
</ab></div><div type="textpart" n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete"><ab part="N">

